# 🏠 Smart Home Project – Week 3 Tasks

## 🎯 Goal of the Week
Integrate all modules together and activate smart features (GUI ↔ Backend ↔ Voice Assistant).

---

## 👥 Team Members and Roles

| Member | Role | Deliverables |
|---------|------|--------------|
| **Diaa** | Integrator | Connect backend logic with GUI (JavaFX Controllers) |
| **Mohamed** | GUI Developer (JavaFX) | Develop Dashboard screen (FXML + Controller) |
| **Ola** | Database Developer | Store device events automatically in DB |
| **Yara** | Logic Developer | Implement Auto Mode (time / temperature based) |
| **Mazen** | Smart Assistant Developer | Add voice commands using FreeTTS |
| **Menna** | Data Analyst | Create Logs & Statistics GUI (JavaFX Charts) |

---

## 📦 Deliverables for Week 3

| File | Description | Responsible |
|---------|-------------|-------------|
| `src/com/smarthome/view/DashboardView.fxml` | Dashboard interface | Mohamed |
| `src/com/smarthome/view/DashboardController.java` | Dashboard controller (device logic) | Mohamed, Diaa |
| `src/com/smarthome/assistant/VoiceAssistant.java` | Voice interface (FreeTTS) | Mazen |
| `src/com/smarthome/analysis/LogsPage.java` | JavaFX chart page for logs | Menna |
| `src/com/smarthome/controller/HomeController.java` | Integrated control logic | Yara, Diaa |
| `src/com/smarthome/database/DatabaseManager.java` | Auto logging of device events | Ola |

